    v2 = (((v1 + 0.97 + tmp + 0.40) - wp.exp(v0 + 0.13)) + wp.cos(wp.exp(v2 + 0.37)))
    v1 = ((wp.sin(v0 + 0.59) - 0.52) / (wp.abs(v0 + 0.70) - (v2 + 0.90 * v2 + 0.32)))
    v0 = wp.sin(wp.abs(v1))
    v2 = v2
    v2 = v0
    v2 = wp.sin(tmp)
